Package: ChainLadder
Type: Package
Title: Mack, Bootstrap, Munich, Multivariate-chain-ladder and Clark methods for insurance claims reserving
Version: 0.1.3-5
Date: 2010-11-03
Author: Markus Gesmann, Wayne (Yanwei) Zhang, Daniel Murphy
Maintainer: Markus Gesmann <markus.gesmann@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides Mack-, Munich-, Bootstrap, and Multivariate-chain-ladder methods, as well as the LDF Curve Fitting methods of Dave Clark. These methods are typically used in insurance claims reserving.
Depends: Hmisc, lattice, Matrix, methods, stats, systemfit, MASS, RUnit
Suggests: RODBC
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://code.google.com/p/chainladder/
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
